snippet.title: Doukutsu Randamu: gameplay showcase
snippet.description:
This video demonstrates the gameplay of Doukutsu Randamu: the Cave Story mod that converts original game into roguelite adventure.
Download it here: https://trashboxbobylev.itch.io/doukutsu-randamu
